# Regression test list schema
# Each non-empty, non-comment line has one of these forms:
#   <test_name>
#   <test_name> | <sim arg 1> <sim arg 2> ...
#
# Notes:
# - Lines starting with # are ignored.
# - Arguments are split by whitespace (basic schema).
# - To pass plusargs, use run_sauria style tokens (e.g. sv_seed=42 or +foo=bar).

